Invocation Name: grandmother names
des: Grandmother Names is a list of fun, traditional, and even regional grandmother names. Every grandmother should have a unique name that her grandchildren call her. This list will help new grandmothers find their own grandmother name. List will be updated periodically as new names are discovered. No additional hardware or anything else required.
